<@1175455408538800205> is there any way for this script to only switch to totem one time when I open my inventory and not spam it? ```def module double-hand-auto-totem
def desc "Custom Scripted Module"

on tick if input_active inventory {
    switch #totem
    gui_quickmove #totem 9
    if off_holding #air,#shield {
        gui_swap #totem
    }
}